OL,3,CMan dies days after being sent home
OL,4,Cfrom A&E with Gaviscon
OL,6,FSandra O'Hagan talks to ITV Granada's
OL,7,FAnna Youssef about the misdiagnosis
OL,8,Fthat led to her partner's death.
OL,10,FA woman who says her partner died
OL,11,Fafter being misdiagnosed and sent home
OL,12,Ffrom A&E with Gaviscon has called for
OL,13,Fgreater awareness about a heart
OL,14,Fcondition that "flies under the radar".
OL,16,FDavid Burgess, 52, had never "taken a
OL,17,Fday off work" and was generally
OL,18,Fhealthy until he experienced
OL,19,F"horrific" stomach and back pain.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
