OL,3,CMan dies days after being sent home
OL,4,Cfrom A&E with Gaviscon
OL,6,F"It didn't seem real. I just thought
OL,7,Fhow can this be happening? How can
OL,8,Fthey have make such a huge mistake? He
OL,9,Fwent to A&E nearly a week ago and they
OL,10,Fsent him home," she said.
OL,12,F'There was such a big gap between the
OL,13,Fdiagnosis of gastritis and aortic
OL,14,Fdissection.
OL,16,F"It just didn't make any sense and I
OL,17,Fcouldn't believe it had got missed in
OL,18,Fa major hospital which is right next
OL,19,Fto the biggest heart centre in the
OL,20,FNorth West. I was angry and upset."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
