OL,3,CMan dies days after being sent home
OL,4,Cfrom A&E with Gaviscon
OL,6,FDavid, a legal recruitment consultant,
OL,7,Fwas diagnosed with gastritis -
OL,8,Finflammation of the stomach lining -
OL,9,Fat Wythenshawe's A&E department.
OL,11,FHe was sent home later that day and
OL,12,Ftold to take Gaviscon - typically used
OL,13,Fto treat heartburn and indigestion -
OL,14,Fwith no follow-up appointment arranged.
OL,16,FSandra, 56, said his pain and symptoms
OL,17,Fpersisted and so he returned to A&E on
OL,18,F1 May, where he was diagnosed with
OL,19,Faortic dissection.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
