OL,3,CMan dies days after being sent home
OL,4,Cfrom A&E with Gaviscon
OL,6,FThe life-threatening condition is
OL,7,Fcharacterised by the tearing of the
OL,8,Faortic wall, which can compromise
OL,9,Fblood flow to vital organs.
OL,11,FAfter urgent surgery, doctors told
OL,12,FSandra there was nothing more they
OL,13,Fcould do and it would be "cruel to
OL,14,Fkeep trying".
OL,16,FHis life-support was withdrawn on 10
OL,17,FMay.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
