OL,3,CMan dies days after being sent home
OL,4,Cfrom A&E with Gaviscon
OL,6,FSandra now wants to raise awareness of
OL,7,FAortic dissections "to prevent other
OL,8,Ffamilies from going through this",
OL,9,Fadding more needs to be done to
OL,10,Feducate people and healthcare
OL,11,Fprofessionals alike.
OL,13,FResearch from the Aortic Dissection
OL,14,FCharitable Trust, the chartered
OL,15,Faccountant added, suggest correct
OL,16,Fdiagnoses could save 10 lives per
OL,17,Fweek, while the charity says 2,000
OL,18,Fpeople a year die from the condition
OL,19,Fin the UK.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
