OL,3,CMan dies days after being sent home
OL,4,Cfrom A&E with Gaviscon
OL,6,FAcute aortic dissection can present
OL,7,Fwith a wide range of symptoms, with
OL,8,Fthe most common being the sudden onset
OL,9,Fof severe pain, typically felt in the
OL,10,Fchest, back, neck or abdomen, or in a
OL,11,Fcombination of these areas.
OL,13,FSandra met David in 2012, describing
OL,14,Fhim as warm, friendly, intelligent and
OL,15,F"very sharp".
OL,17,FWhile she said he struggled with his
OL,18,Fweight, he was otherwise generally
OL,19,Fhealthy and sometimes enjoyed cycling
OL,20,Fto and from work.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
