OL,3,CMan dies days after being sent home
OL,4,Cfrom A&E with Gaviscon
OL,6,F"He never went to the doctors, and I
OL,7,Fcan't remember him taking a day off
OL,8,Fwork - he was always so committed to
OL,9,Fworking and he was pretty tough," she
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FOn 24 April, however, he told Sandra
OL,13,Fhe was experiencing a "sharp pain" in
OL,14,Fhis stomach and back.
OL,16,FSince it was not in his chest, they
OL,17,Fdid not think it was heart related.
OL,19,F"He said he'd never felt anything like
OL,20,Fit before," she explained.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
