OL,3,CMan dies days after being sent home
OL,4,Cfrom A&E with Gaviscon
OL,6,F"It was absolutely horrific, just
OL,7,Fcompletely out of nowhere.
OL,9,F"Aortic dissection seems to be flying
OL,10,Funder the radar... but this awareness
OL,11,Fis so important and something's got to
OL,12,Fbe done."
OL,14,FWhat are the symptoms of an aortic
OL,15,Fdissection?
OL,17,FAccording to the British Heart
OL,18,FFoundation symptoms can include:
