OL,6,FIf you have any of these symptoms, you
OL,7,Fshould immediately call 999 because it
OL,8,Fneeds urgent treatment.
OL,10,FSandra is also exploring legal action
OL,11,Fagainst the hospital, although
OL,12,Finvestigations were currently ongoing.
OL,14,FJackie Linehan, Enable Law legal
OL,15,Fdirector and Ms O'Hagan's solicitor,
OL,16,Fwho is working with aortic dissection
OL,17,Fcharities, said: "Aortic dissection if
OL,18,Fcaught at the right time can in some
OL,19,Fcases be treatable.
