OL,6,F"Therefore it's really important that
OL,7,Fit's diagnosed early so we're looking
OL,8,Fat whether that's the case for David
OL,9,Fand whether had he been investigated
OL,10,Fand diagnosed properly when he
OL,11,Fattended hospital whether he could've
OL,12,Fhad surgery at that point and that
OL,13,Fwould've save his life."
OL,15,FA Manchester University NHS Foundation
OL,16,FTrust spokesperson offered "sincere
OL,17,Fcondolences to Mr Burgess's family and
OL,18,Ffriends for their loss", and said his
OL,19,Fcare was being reviewed.
