OL,6,FA spokesperson said: "We have
OL,7,Fdiscussed his sad death with Ms
OL,8,FO'Hagan, and we are undertaking a
OL,9,Freview of Mr Burgess's care."
OL,11,F"Findings from that review will be
OL,12,Fshared with both Ms O'Hagan and the
OL,13,Fcoroner", the trust spokesperson added.
OL,15,FThe trust was awaiting the conclusion
OL,16,Fof the inquest before commenting
OL,17,Ffurther.
